===============================================================================
                    OCCUPATIONAL CHARACTER CLASSES (OCCs)
===============================================================================

AetherMUD features 36 Occupational Character Classes:

MEN-OF-ARMS (Combat Specialists):
  cyber_knight          - High-tech paladin (psionic warrior)
  glitter_boy_pilot     - Iconic power armor pilot
  headhunter            - Freelance mercenary (combat expert)
  juicer                - Chemical augmentation warrior (short lifespan)
  mercenary             - Soldier for hire
  special_forces        - Elite military operative
  wilderness_scout      - Ranger/tracker (survival expert)
  cosmo_knight          - Cosmic champion (divine power)

SCHOLARS & ADVENTURERS:
  body_fixer            - Combat medic/cyberdoc
  city_rat              - Urban survivor (street smart)
  rogue_scholar         - Researcher/historian
  rogue_scientist       - Independent scientist
  vagabond              - Jack-of-all-trades wanderer
  operator              - Mechanic/technician (repairs everything)

PSYCHICS:
  burster               - Pyrokinetic (master of fire)
  mind_melter           - Master psychic (full psionics)
  psi_healer            - Healing specialist
  crazy                 - Enhanced psychotic (MOM implants)

PRACTITIONERS OF MAGIC:
  ley_line_walker       - Classic mage (ley line magic)
  line_walker           - Ley line specialist
  mystic                - Natural magic user (intuitive)
  shifter               - Dimensional traveler (summoner)
  warlock               - Elemental magic (pact magic)
  techno_wizard         - Technology + magic fusion
  necromancer           - Death magic specialist
  battle_magus          - Warrior-mage hybrid
  biomancer             - Life magic specialist
  elemental_fusionist   - Elemental combination master
  stone_master          - Earth/stone magic
  temporal_wizard       - Time manipulation mage

SPECIAL OCCs:
  full_conversion_borg  - Full cybernetic conversion (machine body)
  power_armor_pilot     - Power armor specialist
  robot_pilot           - Robot/mecha pilot
  dragon_hatchling_rcc  - Young dragon (racial class)
  sea_titan             - Aquatic titan being
  psi_stalker           - Psionic predator (anti-mage)

===============================================================================
To see details on a specific OCC: help <occ_name>
Example: help cyber_knight, help ley_line_walker, help juicer

For OCC categories:
  help men-at-arms     - Combat specialists
  help scholars        - Educated/skilled classes
  help psychics        - Psionic classes
  help magic           - Magic-using classes
===============================================================================
